## About the Project

*3D Print Project*

This is a project about how every factor of a 3D print can change how strong and how high quality it is, and examining the relationships between them.

This project was made as part of 
[Kane's Free High School Data Science Bootcamp](https://bootcamp.davidkane.info/)
